cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CL, cs.LG 

The paper focuses on incorporating vision and language modeling with common-sense knowledge for autonomous robotics. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a systematic scheme to generate knowledge graphs, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques, indicating that it could also belong to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
